  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_6' aria-label=\" Arabian Exports Private Limited versus National Insurance Company Ltd. pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('6','2025','2025_5_798_813','2025INSC630'); ><font size='4'> <strong>ARABIAN EXPORTS PRIVATE LIMITED<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>NATIONAL INSURANCE COMPANY LTD. </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 5 S.C.R. 798</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 630</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010004322025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : ABHAY S. OKA<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, UJJAL BHUYAN</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Whether a dispute raised by an insured after giving a full and final discharge voucher to the insurer can be referred to arbitration. Headnotes&dagger; Arbitration and Conciliation Act, 1996 &ndash; s.11 &ndash; Appellant claimed loss and damages under the insurance &ndash; After a considerable delay, a grossly inadequate amount was offered by the respondent &ndash; Due to financial strain, appellant signed the undated and standardized voucher/advance receipt &ndash; Pursuant thereto, appellant received the cheque issued by the respondent &ndash;<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 06-05-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CIVIL APPEAL No. 6372/2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Appeal(s) allowed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('6','2025','2025_5_798_813','2025INSC630','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('6','2025','2025_5_798_813','2025INSC630','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('6','2025','2025_5_798_813','2025INSC630');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('6','2025','2025_5_798_813','2025INSC630','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
